author: quintonm
msg: Basic testing of the dynamicURI class.  The only testing involved currently it to make sure that
moving pathInfo or queryData does not result in a ConcurrentModificationException

author: quintonm
msg: Removing elements from pathInfo and queryData is now done by calling the remove()
method of the iterator.  This addresses a ConcurrentModificationException that was
occurring when and element was removed.
